snippet.textDisplay: MAX respect to Coke Studio for letting us play freely in their playground! Honestly, we were super skeptical about sending the first draft of the remix, wondering if the team would find it commercial enough for a global platform. However, we quickly realized this is COKE STUDIO—they're known for breaking the rules, bringing the edge, and always delivering something fresh. And just like that, a dream was realised & our version found a home at Coke Studio :)
